=== Bester Film ===

Oscar für '''[[Das Leben des Emile Zola]] (The Life of Emile Zola) – [[Warner Bros.]]'''
:[[100 Mann und ein Mädchen]] ''(One Hundred Men and a Girl)'' – [[Universal Pictures|Universal]]
:[[Manuel (Film)|Manuel]] ''(Captain Courageous)'' – [[Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer]]
:[[In den Fesseln von Shangri-La]] ''(Lost Horizon)'' – [[Columbia Pictures|Columbia]]
:[[Die gute Erde (Film)|Die gute Erde]] ''(The Good Earth)'' – [[Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer]]
:[[Die schreckliche Wahrheit]] ''(The Awful Truth)'' – [[Columbia Pictures|Columbia]]
:[[Sackgasse (Film)|Sackgasse]] ''(Dead End)'' – [[Samuel Goldwyn]] Productions
:[[Ein Stern geht auf]] ''(A Star is Born)'' – [[David O. Selznick|Selznick International Pictures]]
:[[In Old Chicago]] – [[20th Century Fox]]
:[[Bühneneingang]] ''(Stage Door)'' – [[RKO Radio]]

